Sharon Osbourne Exposes Amber Heard & Johnny Depp | InformOverload

Sharon Osbourne has voiced her opinions regarding the Johnny Depp, Amber Heard case, in which Johnny lost the libel suit against the Publication the Sun, for referring to Depp as a wife beater. Following the surprising outcome, which has also led to Depp being removed from the third Fantastic Beasts film, Johnny as well as his legal team have made it clear they are going to appeal the outcome.
